    <stitle>POWER STEERING GEAR: SHEPPARD M-SERIES - PREVENTIVE MAINTENANCE</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcsubsec>
        <title>PREVENTIVE MAINTENANCE</title>
        <svcsubsecinfo>
            <para>Fluid and filter change is necessary to keep the fluid in the system clean. Refer to TYPES OF FLUID
                below for the correct fluid and change intervals for the model vehicle being serviced.
            </para>
            <specpara>
                <important>
                    <para>Never use old or used seals, cotter pins, retainers or critical fasteners. Always use a new
                        seal kit. Use only International approved replacement parts.
                    </para>
                </important>
            </specpara>
        </svcsubsecinfo>
    </svcsubsec>
